    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Ghostly spirits emerge from your body and whirl around you. Your body emits dim light in a 15-foot radius for the spellâ€™s duration. Until the spell ends, you gain the following benefits:<ul><li>You have immunity to necrotic damage and resistance to poison damage.</li><li>Creatures that miss on melee attacks against you become frightened of you until the end of their next turn.</li><li>You can use an action to direct the ghostly spirits to assail a creature you can see within 15 feet of you. The target must make a successful Constitution saving throw or take 2d10 necrotic damage and gain one level of exhaustion.</li><br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl-bf.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
